$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
change_movezones

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
change_movezones -  This method changes the value of the move zones for the specified room and directory.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void change_movezones(string dir,
string room,
string * zones)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^dir%^RESET%^ - the directory to change the values in
%^BOLD%^room%^RESET%^ - the room the change the values in
%^BOLD%^zones%^RESET%^ - the new set of move zones
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method changes the value of the move zones for the specified
room and directory.
.EP

